extendedInfo.description: Enter the world of epic hunting carnivore Dino World!The rules of dinosaurs overpower the world of dark forces. But this would be fun to play with. Dino World enlightens your child with numerous details of dinosaurs. Short yet charming intakes of carnivore creatures kids story; which lets them grow a good habit of reading in the early days of their childhood. Reading along with visual aid makes your children mesmerized and intrigued to learn more. This app connects your curious kids to the encyclopedia that holds selected illustrations of various species of dinosaurs and educates them about the facts: length, what food they ate, fossil locations (where were the fossils found), and time. By this repetition your kids can learn quickly and memorize everything about dinosaurs easily. This App is exclusively designed for Toddlers, babies, Preschool, Kindergarten and First Grader Kids.***Features***â An exclusive kids storyâ An encyclopedia of Dinosaursâ A fun filled memory match gameâ A coloring book for kidsâ High quality imagesâ Colorful cards and flip animations in memory match gameâ Three different size brushes available for kids to use and color withâ A wide range of Dynamic colors to choose while coloringâ Eraser tool to help you remove messed up colors and the Clear All button that cleans up all by itself while you sit back.â New and improve finger drawing method to enhance the game play instead of that old technique of tap and paint.â Tic-Toc timer to challenge the speed at which your kids are playingâ Time at the end tells how fast you completed the rack.Enjoy this free app with an exclusive kids story, a memory match game, a coloring book to color & paint and facts about dinosaurs. It comes in 11 languages (Arabic, Chinese, Dutch, English, French, German, Italian, Japanese, Russian, Spanish, Portuguese), depends whichever you choose. Try this fun filled app apart from all those cooking and maker apps that you love to play. This app will let you learn with fun. We love to hear from you so tell us about your experiences and suggestions to help us keep working on apps for your kids to help them gain knowledge and learning.***DISCLAIMER***â This free app is ad supported and may contain ads in the notification tray and/or home screen.
